    **DESIGN INVARIANT CRITICAL NOTE**: The line `// Canonical Document container field is sprk_graphdriveid; sprk_containerid stays NULL on sprk_document (design.md INV)` MUST be present in the modified code. Phase F backfill depends on `sprk_document.sprk_containerid` being NULL universally — adding it here would corrupt the backfill audit downstream.

